{"tid":1057711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2中國人向引擎掟硬幣　260旅客無辜被拖累","createTime":"2019-03-12T05:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T07:40:23.000Z","uid":41404,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"888bb637c78d985752bfb8cb39dc528c82197606","tid":1057711,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"中國不時發生乘客搭飛機時，投幣祈福的無知行為，給航行安全帶來威脅。周日（10日）晚上，祥鵬航空8L9616山東濟南至四川成都航班的2名年輕女旅客，登機時向引擎方向投擲硬幣，導致航班延誤2個小時，260名旅客受影響。 <br />\n<br />\n該航空公司稱，乘務員在旅客過站登機時，發現有兩名20多歲的女子向廊橋外掟硬幣，當時旅客隨即被移交機場公安。隨後航班安全員在廊橋下發現兩枚硬幣，與2名女子向警員供述向廊橋縫隙處，各自掟出一枚一元硬幣的說法吻合。 <br />\n<br />\n另經機長現場觀察，廊橋與飛機鏈接處僅有一道狹小縫隙且距離發動機較遠，評估認為無將硬幣扔進發動機的風險，最終該航班在延誤至當晚10時02分起飛。至於2名女旅客目前已被移交公安機關處理。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190312/mobile/bkn-20190312130113435-0312_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190312%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190312130113435-0312_00952_001.html&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6JMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=c524a077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190312/mobile/bkn-20190312130113435-0312_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e774a4fd9ccbbecb5cf1a4c010dbff2ef20e9c59","tid":1057711,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba54b5f8daf9b409438df5ba64609fa2aa9960ff","tid":1057711,"uid":3063,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"難得肯睇下<br />\n唔撚睇 飛上天就爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6074304521d4c205240330d929ad6ff7ae65973","tid":1057711,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"old new ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdd5c3108846a6ce4022d